phrases: Operation: Infiltrate a Planetoid Base
They are fast!
I cannot process their data quick enough!
My unit feels heavy!
Did it get fat?!
Did it?!
There is gravity since we are on Earth!
Crap!
I cannot keep up with them!
Guys, get your acts together!
Your controls will go bonkers if you panic!
Right back at you!
Is not that Team Rabbits?
Supposedly their AHSMB units are under repair.
Since they are still considered students, they are getting a supplementary lesson.
Is it just me, or do they suck even worse now?
Who are the other three?
Probably teachers.
Students cannot pull off moves like those.
I have got to do something!
Now that it is come to this...!
Shining Miracle Turn Smash!
What gives?
What the hell was that?
And here I put my faith in you!
Fine!
I will charge ahead!
Whoo boy...
Their formation is a mess...
What the heck was that Miracle-whatever?
My secret move.
Yeah, figures.
Most heroes have a secret move, do not they?
I know, right?
We do not need one!
But heroes use secret moves to save the day.
I was sure I could pull it off...
If all we needed was confidence, we would get 100's studying by ourselves!
I never got to show my stuff...
Yo!
You were not looking too hot out there, huh?
Freakin' out after that string of losses?
Your training session is over.
Team Rabbits, everyone is to submit your
own personal analysis on why you lost.
Assemble in the Meeting Room in 30 minutes with Team Doberman.
Over.
See ya later.
Sirs, thank you for the lesson!
That is Team Doberman for ya!
They are scary!
Were not they also students here?
Supposedly they were highly accomplished.
A joint meeting...
Does that mean we are working with them on our next mission?
That would be super awesome!
All three dudes are stud muffins!
I am amazed you can act so carefree
after nearly getting killed in that last mission.
Fear and romance are two different things!
Man!
I guess the Fail Five are still the Fail Five, huh?
How come they get to pilot cutting-edge fighters?
My entrance may come surprisingly soon...
I thought my Likeability Stats would go up after becoming a wee bit famous.
You cannot blame them for feeling that way.
When you get down to it, our team only won that very first battle.
They are blasting us on the internet again...
Do not bring that up.
You will give me another ulcer.
Your AHSMB units have been fully repaired.
You will be transferring to Star Rose tomorrow.
Upon arrival, we will commence a co-op mission.
What is the matter?
Madam, what if we fail again...?
Thinking like that will only hinder your performance!
You will be fine!
This time you have got Team Doberman with you.
Lt. Commander, I have a question!
I have been meaning to ask this for some time.
Go ahead, Lieutenant.
Please tell me your personal address and when you are off duty.
Randy, we are in the middle of a meeting!
You should not ask such shameless questions.
Do not be such a stiff!
If ya do not ask stuff like this when you can,
you could forever miss the boat!
With you as our clown of a leader,
people keep calling us the Bummer Three,
the Comedic Three and Trio Dobermans.
The Bummer Three?
Just what I would expect from our seniors!
What is wrong with being the Bummer Three?!
And why do you always act like you are better than me?!
Just because we are classmates does not mean you can walk all over me!
It is the sub-leader's job to guide the leader down the right path.
What are you, the disciplinary committee?!
Pardon?
Why must you always act so cool?!
What are you going on about in the middle of a meeting?
Do you think you are on the Cool Committee?!
Sorry, but I do not have time to play.
You should try to act a bit more like a leader!
Wh-what?!
If there are no further questions, this meeting is adjourned.
I am sorry.
My team always acts like this.
I-I see...
Quit acting like you are excluded from our antics!
Ow, that hurts!
Randy!
I give up!
Uncle, uncle!
Thank God they are not as scary as I thought.
What was that?
I could not hear you?
In fact, they are funny.
You want me to stop?
But they are still cool!
And they saved our hides!
They are totally the hero type!
I will really let you have it next time!
I swear, you never change!
Neither do you!
Excuse me!
Thank you for saving me the other day.
Uh, are not you Red 5's pilot...?
I am Izuru Hitachi.
It feels like ages since I was here last.
You have got it rough, huh?
They are sending you out hunting when you are still just a student.
People are going to say what they are going to say; do not worry'bout it.
But I do!
Whenever I get sent to battle, I wonder if I am doing enough.
You have survived this far!
Is not that good enough?
But I want to become a hero!
A hero?
So?
Why do you want to be a hero of all things?
Because I think they are great!
I-I see...
All right.
I will tell you what it takes to be a hero.
You must be...
Good looking?
Right, it is all about the looks!
To be a hero, you got to be the best looking
member in your group and get all of the girls.
Are not I a prime example?
Y-yeah...
For the record, you...
Yeah, you are not as handsome as me, but you are plenty good looking!
Do not worry, you will become an amazing hero.
I guarantee it!
Is-is that right...?
Let us see, what else is there...?
Making decisions, never giving up and believing in your comrades.
Do you trust them... your friends?
I watched the footage from all of Team Rabbits' battles so far.
You try to do everything yourself while
desperately fighting to protect your friends.
You cannot keep a team together if you do not believe in your men!
Now putting that aside!
The pilots for Unit 2 and Unit 3...
Which do you have your sights set on?
Pardon?
Are not they both adorable?
Which is your type?
Or are you already dating one of them?!
I-I could not possibly!
We are a team, so that sort of stuff is taboo!
What?!
I cannot believe my ears!
Just how old are you guys?
Kei, Suruga and I are 16.
Asagi is 17.
Tamaki is 15.
These are the best days of your life!
You got to fall in love, squabble and then break up!
I really cannot do that!
I know!
Swap teams with me.
As of today, you are Team Doberman's leader; I am taking Rabbits.
What?!
Of course, I am just pulling your leg.
Your eyes looked kind of serious...
Listen.
In our line of work, you never know when you are going to die.
Would not you like someone to remember
who you were after you are gone?
Interact with as many people as you possibly can.
And make sure you remember each person you meet along the way.
You can borrow this.
Study this with the pilots for Unit 1 and Unit 4.
Does it contain footage from our battles?
Close enough.
Watch this and put your best foot forward!
I will!
Let us watch this together!
What is it?
Does it contain video records?
Yep!
He said to only watch it with Asagi and Suruga,
but I figured we could all watch it together!
What is this...?
That hurt...!
What the hell are you thinking?!
Well, this is not exactly what I was expecting...
Pro wrestling?
Wh-what?
What?
Wh-what is the big deal?!
This is a bit much for me...
Why are you freaking out when you are the one constantly flirting with the ladies?
B-but this is on a totally different level...
I am going to pass!
Damn it!
If we get caught, reports will be the least of our worries.
But I did not mean-
Enough!
This is truly ridiculous.
I just realized something important.
What is it?
This actress resembles Instructor Suzukaze.
Now that you mention it, I can see that...
I cannot bear to watch!
The mission's name is Operation: MacLean.
You are to infiltrate the enemy base on Planetoid RA221 and blow it up.
Concentrate!
Sir, what do you think has gotten into them?
Beats me.
We do not know what to expect once you are in.
Although it is not terribly big,
we believe the base's artificial gravity device is active.
We have outfitted your units for fighting in gravity.
Was our training on Earth before the mission
meant to serve as a simulation?
It is far enough away from the battlefield that we expect minimal security.
However, with weak transmission signals,
it will be impossible to communicate with us.
Gold 4 will be in charge of the bomb.
You will also use Gold 4's computer to detonate it.
This mission came out of nowhere, did not it?
I cannot believe we are destroying a base that is on the sidelines.
They are probably trying to make the other team look good.
That is what it would take to save the MJP's face.
At any rate, they want evidence that we are winning.
I bet this is a co-op to increase the chances of success.
Yeah, but do you think we can handle this...?
Did you end up watching that video last night?
Not me!
I did not watch it!
Kei, are you going to tell the instructor...?
No, I would not do that!
D-do not worry, Kei!
I am sleepy after staying up all night,
but it was really refreshing.
Well?
Was it a good picker upper?
Yeah, but I wound up showing it to Kei and Tamaki...
What?!
Y-you have got some balls!
I am amazed you have treaded grounds far more dangerous than I have!
G-gee, thanks...
Identifying the enemy base.
I am forwarding the image.
What is going on here?!
Were not we expecting minimal security?
What should we do?
Withdraw and request new orders?
We cannot reach our commanding officers.
We will have to make the call for ourselves...
Let us carry out the mission!
If the base is crowded with enemies when it should not be,
it means they are up to something.
We cannot go back empty-handed!
Roger!
Crap!
They found us.
But how?
Do they have eyes and ears?
We will take them on!
My team will draw the enemy fire
while your team carries out the mission!
But will you be okay?!
Do not worry about us!
There should be a gravity reactor at the center of the base.
Set the bomb there.
You will do fine as long as you remain calm.
They want us to infiltrate the base by ourselves...?
My feet absolutely refuse to move!
Do not run away!
Use your willpower to rein in the JURIA-SYSTEM's survival instincts!
Go!
Y-yes, sir!
Let us go, Red 5!
L-let us fight!
Follow me, Purple 2!
H-hey, wait!
What will we do if they find us again?
Doberman is attracting all of the enemy's attention.
We will be fine...
I think... maybe.
It looks like the base's guards still do not know we are here.
I bet we could get in through there.
Rose 3 cannot fit through that entrance.
What?!
What should we do, Izuru?
Leave Tamaki behind?
Make up your mind before the gate closes!
I will stay behind.
Asagi...!
We will probably need to shoot down any enemy fighters that come back.
Do not worry.
We can handle it!
Thank you.
Kei, Suruga, let us go!
So this is a Wulgaru base...
I am detecting a reactor located 250 meters below us.
If we blow that up, it should take out the entire base.
And the route?
Straight ahead.
Enemy fighters incoming at 2:00!
Suruga, protect the bomb!
Kei, can you activate the defense shields?
I could, but they will make scanning and analyzing the area that much harder.
Got it.
Then we will plow through without them!
Good thing we trained on Earth!
Take the upcoming 90 turn to the right!
Next drop 90 vertically down!
The heat values are higher than I had anticipated.
The sudden fluctuation in heat is beginning to interfere with my sensors.
Can you at least tell what direction it is in?
If we follow the artificial gravity pipeline, we should reach the source.
Does not that mean we are going to keep falling for who knows how long?!
They are not holding back even though we are inside their base!
That is a given!
If we destroy this reactor, it will send the whole base sky high!
It got hit somewhere along the line!
Crap!
I cannot set it like this.
What?!
The mission's a failure!
We got to retreat.
Retreat!
What should we do, Izuru?
Izuru!
Suruga, can you fix it?
I do not think it is beyond me...
Then do it!
We will not make it back alive if we do not destroy this base.
This is our only option if we hope to survive this!
Are you serious?!
Suruga, you can do it!
I believe in you!
Izuru!
Kei, use your shields to protect Suruga.
I will distract the enemy!
Darn!
I guess this is the only way.
We are going to survive...
Everyone is!
I wonder if everyone is okay...
Yeah...
They will come back safe and sound.
Otherwise my stomach will kill me!
Hurry up, Suruga!
Izuru is...!
It is all set!
I am a genius!
Great!
Now let us withdraw.
It worked!
Sweet!
The secondary explosions are going off fast!
We will get caught in the blast if we do not hurry!
Why?!
What type of energy are they using?!
We will not make it...!
I suddenly accelerated!
The instinct to survive means serious business!
Tamaki, thank you!
Honestly, you three are lost without me.
Is everyone okay?
Asagi!
I was so sure I was going to die this time...
Lookin' good there...
Hero of the Day!
Graduation
